{ 4-Suit Jacoby Transfers - Transfer to Minors }
^-|AT|^B@2^Y@3One variant of Jacoby that I use is 4-suit Jacoby transfer. A 2@S bid by responder is a transfer to clubs, and a 2NT bid is a transfer to diamonds. Since there are two bids between the transfer bid and the transfer suit, opener now has two choices. |
