AT|

@SKxxx @HQxx @DKQxxx @Cx
You have maximum. You want to see if you have a 4-4 spade fit, Bid 2@C. Over a 2@S response, bid 4@S. Over any other response bid 3N. Remember, if partner responded 2@H and also had a 4-card spade suit, partner can correct 3N to 4@S.|
